metadata.name: Space Between
metadata.description:
The start of a journey always begin with a clear intention. The space between belief and doubt will disappear when our mind is set to the right and clear purpose.

So, what is the purpose of the journey?
"To find peace and serenity..."

300 dpi

Hand-drawing on Adobe Photoshop
